## Dependencies List

**Expo Managed**
- `expo-router` — file-based navigation
- `expo-linking` — deep linking
- `expo-constants` — app config/env variables
- `expo-status-bar` — status bar control
- `expo-location` — GPS/geolocation (live tracking, 5-second updates)
- `expo-notifications` — local notification scheduling
- `expo-auth-session` — OAuth (Google/Apple)
- `expo-web-browser` — required by auth-session
- `expo-image-picker` — before/after photo uploads by provider
- `expo-file-system` — file handling
- `expo-camera` — in-app camera for provider photo capture during active job
- `expo-secure-store` — secure storage for auth tokens

**Supabase**
- `@supabase/supabase-js` — database, auth, realtime, storage
- `@react-native-async-storage/async-storage` — session persistence

**Payments**
- `@stripe/stripe-react-native` — Stripe Connect, deposits, balance capture

**State Management**
- `zustand` — global state stores
- React Context — built-in, no package required; feature-scoped localized state

**Maps & Location**
- `react-native-maps` — live GPS map, provider tracking, service location pin
- `@googlemaps/js-api-loader` — Google Maps SDK integration

**Notifications**
- `@react-native-firebase/app` — Firebase core (required by FCM)
- `@react-native-firebase/messaging` — Firebase Cloud Messaging for push

**Analytics & Monitoring**
- `mixpanel-react-native` — funnel analysis, retention tracking
- `@sentry/react-native` — crash reporting, performance monitoring

**UI & Animation**
- `react-native-reanimated` — spring-based animations
- `react-native-gesture-handler` — required by Reanimated and sheets
- `nativewind` — Tailwind for React Native
- `tailwindcss` — required by NativeWind
- `lucide-react-native` — base icon library

**Utilities**
- `ioredis` — Redis client (GPS caching, rate limiting, short-lived tokens)
- `date-fns` — date formatting